column2: [ComA + CcpA + TnrA] / [Abh + SigA + ComA + Spx + PhoP + CodY + PerR]
[ComA + CcpA + TnrA]  or  [Abh + SigA + ComA + Spx + PhoP + CodY + PerR]
Activated during transition to stationary phase (quorum sensing), production of surfactant and exoenzymes to improve nutrient delivery in the biofilm, ComS for activation of competence
